section#story
    .container.py-lg-5
        .row.align-items-center
            .col-12
                h6.top-title Our Story
                h3.title What Make Us Different
            .col-lg-6.story-left
                .pe-lg-4
                    p.text-muted.mb-3
                        | At Cabo San Lucas Rides, we believe that transportation is not just about moving from one point to another; it is the first and last impression of your journey. Since 2021, we have curated every detail to ensure your travel experience reflects the luxury and tranquility of the Baja.
                    p.text-muted.mb-3
                        | Our philosophy is built on the perfect balance of local hospitality and executive precision. We don’t just drive; we navigate with intention, ensuring your comfort is never compromised.
                    p.text-muted
                        | Simply premium. Simply on time.
            .col-lg-6.story-right
                .d-flex.flex-column.gap-4.ps-lg-4
                    .storycard.card
                        .d-flex.gap-4.align-items-start
                            div
                                h5 The Fleet
                                h6 THE PINNACLE OF COMFORT
                                p
                                    | Modern, meticulously maintained vehicles. From executive SUVs to luxury vans, our fleet is the silent engine of your peace of mind.
                    .storycard.card
                        .d-flex.gap-4.align-items-start
                            div
                                h5 The Chauffeurs
                                h6 MASTERS OF THE ROAD
                                p
                                    | Bilingual experts with deep local knowledge. They control time and logistics with the calm of a seasoned professional, ensuring safety in every mile.
                    .storycard.card
                        .d-flex.gap-4.align-items-start
                            div
                                h5 The Service
                                h6 ARCHITECTS OF EXPERIENCE
                                p
                                    | Tailored logistics that map your needs. We manage the variables of arrival times and routes so you can focus on the beauty of Los Cabos.
style.
    section#story { background-color: #{color1}; padding-top: 3rem !important; padding-bottom: 3rem !important; }
    section#story .storycard { background-color: #{color3}; border: 0; border-radius: 20px; padding: 1.5rem !important }
    section#story .storycard h5 { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700 !important; margin-bottom: 0 !important; }
    section#story .storycard h6 { color: #{color5}; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; }
    section#story .storycard p { color: #{color6}; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; }
    .ls-2 { letter-spacing: 2px; }
